      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>''I prepared him for the Americans and let them take his confession. We know how to make them talk. We know their back streets. We beat them.''</p>
        <p>CAPT. BASSIM HASSAN, an Iraqi Army officer, on the treatment of a suspected insurgent. [1]</p>
